&lt;p&gt;By applying for this job, the candidate acknowledges and agrees that any personal data contained in their application or supporting materials will be processed in accordance with &lt;a class=&quot;c-link c-link--underline&quot; href=&quot;https://www.figma.com/legal/candidate-privacy-notice/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.figma.com/legal/candidate-privacy-notice/&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;Figma&#39;s Candidate Privacy Notice&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Figma is growing our team of passionate creatives and builders on a mission to make design accessible to all. Figma’s platform helps teams bring ideas to life—whether you&#39;re brainstorming, creating a prototype, translating designs into code, or iterating with AI. From idea to product, Figma empowers teams to streamline workflows, move faster, and work together in real time from anywhere in the world. If you&#39;re excited to shape the future of design and collaboration, join us!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for a senior leader who thrives on building from first principles, operationalizing creativity, and transforming qualitative experiences into quantitative business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll partner deeply with regional sales leaders, product marketing, demand gen, and the executive team to set the direction for how we activate our community and expand our footprint in-market. You’ll also be a visible voice for the team who regularly presents results, insights, and innovation strategies at company All Hands, leadership offsites, and team meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time role that can be held from one of our US hubs or remotely in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What you’ll do at Figma:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and evolve the global field marketing vision including how we reach and convert accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect repeatable, measurable systems for pipeline influence &amp;amp; ROI tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspire excellence, foster creative experimentation, and ensure accountability to measurable outcomes across a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the connective tissue between marketing, sales, and product. Build deep relationships with regional VPs and senior execs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring data to life by translating complex metrics and campaign outcomes into compelling narratives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pilot new program types, technologies, and experiences that expand what field marketing can be&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As our footprint expands, build the operational infrastructure, team structure, and playbooks that allow Figma’s field programs to grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;We’d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in B2B or PLG marketing, with significant time leading field marketing, experiential, or executive experiences at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of building strategic frameworks for measurement and ROI that shaped executive decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort leading both vision and execution, architecting a global strategy, while not being afraid to roll up your sleeves when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success cultivating trusted partnerships with senior sales leaders and executives, with the confidence and poise to influence at the C-level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep experience turning insights into stories - bringing numbers, outcomes, and customer impact to life through clear and inspiring communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A growth mindset approach to experimentation, iteration, and constantly look for ways to innovate, automate, and scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;While it’s not required, it’s an added plus if you also have:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in a demand generation or account-based marketing position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background running customer advisory boards and executive briefing centers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience creating programming and content narratives across event types&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
